---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const post = { title: 'Corrugated Cardboard Sheets for Trade Show & Exhibition Booths — Lightweight Modular Displays Malaysia', description: 'Build professional trade show booths with corrugated cardboard sheets. Lightweight, paintable, fully recyclable displays for Malaysian exhibitors and event planners.', date: '2026-04-23', readTime: '7 min', category: 'Corrugated Cardboard', author: 'Quinocycle Team', slug: 'corrugated-cardboard-exhibition-booth-0423' };
const WA_LINK = 'https://wa.me/60168916381?text=Hi%20Quinocycle!%20I%20need%20corrugated%20sheets%20for%20an%20exhibition%20booth.';
const articleSchema = { "@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article", headline: post.title, description: post.description, datePublished: '2026-04-23', dateModified: '2026-04-23', inLanguage:"en-MY", author:{name:"Quinocycle Team",url:"https://www.quinocycle.com.my"}, publisher:{name:"Quinocycle Sdn. Bhd.",logo:{url:"https://www.quinocycle.com.my/logo.png"}}, mainEntityOfPage:{url:"https://www.quinocycle.com.my/blog/corrugated-cardboard-exhibition-booth-0423"}, keywords:"exhibition booth cardboard Malaysia, trade show display sheets, modular booth panels, corrugated cardboard event display, lightweight booth Selangor, recyclable trade show Malaysia" };
const faqSchema = { "@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Can corrugated cardboard hold up a full exhibition booth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Double-wall and triple-wall corrugated sheets can be engineered into self-supporting booth walls up to 2.4m tall. Slot-and-tab joinery eliminates the need for glue. Well-designed cardboard booths support modest shelves and display loads."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I print graphics on cardboard booth panels?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Three options: direct flexo printing on the sheets (for large orders), wheat-paste posters applied on-site, or Velcro-mounted vinyl graphics for reusable panels. We can advise on which suits your booth run."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Are cardboard booths fire-safe for Malaysian exhibition venues?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Standard corrugated is flammable. For venues requiring fire-retardant displays (MITEC, KLCC), we supply FR-treated sheets that meet Class B fire-rating requirements. Always confirm with your venue's safety officer."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How affordable is a cardboard booth versus a traditional one?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A full 3x3m cardboard booth costs RM 1,500–3,000 in materials versus RM 8,000+ for a traditional wood/MDF booth. Set-up takes 1–2 hours by two people. Perfect for one-off exhibitions."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I reuse a cardboard booth across multiple shows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes — well-designed booths with protective storage last 5–8 shows. Flat-pack storage between events prevents creasing. Quinocycle supplies replacement panels as needed."}}]};
const localBusinessSchema = { "@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Store", name:"Quinocycle Sdn. Bhd.", url:"https://www.quinocycle.com.my", telephone:"+60168916381", address:{streetAddress:"No.13, Jalan Taming P/1, Taming Jaya", addressLocality:"Balakong", addressRegion:"Selangor", postalCode:"43300", addressCountry:"MY"}, geo:{latitude:3.0579,longitude:101.7468}, openingHoursSpecification:[{dayOfWeek:["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"],opens:"09:00",closes:"18:00"},{dayOfWeek:"Saturday",opens:"09:00",closes:"13:00"}], priceRange:"RM 1.90 – RM 6.50 per box", areaServed:"Peninsular Malaysia" };
---
<Layout title={post.title} description={post.description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(articleSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(localBusinessSchema)} />
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 pt-16 pb-24">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary font-label font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{post.category}</span>
        <time class="font-body text-sm text-secondary">{post.date}</time>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-4">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed">{post.description}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Trade show season in Malaysia is punishing on SMEs and startups. A conventional booth at KLCC or MITEC costs RM 6,000–15,000 once you factor in wood structure, electrics, and labour. Corrugated cardboard sheet booths are quietly revolutionising the exhibition game — strong enough to hold graphics and product shelves, light enough for two people to set up, and affordable enough that first-time exhibitors can afford to show up with a real presence.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Why Cardboard Booths Are Winning in Malaysia</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Cost Cut of 60–75% Versus Wood</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">A 3x3m standard exhibition stand requires roughly 40 sheets of double-wall corrugated at a material cost of RM 1,500–2,500. Compared to RM 6,000+ for a wood-framed equivalent, this lets SMEs allocate budget toward lead-gen, giveaways, and booth staff training instead.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Ultra-Fast Set-Up and Breakdown</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Well-designed slot-and-tab cardboard booths need no tools. Two staff can assemble a 3x3m booth in under 90 minutes. Tear-down is 30 minutes. Compare that to the half-day set-up and full-day build for traditional exhibition stands.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Recyclable and Sustainability-Friendly</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Malaysian corporate buyers increasingly favour sustainability-themed exhibitors. A fully recyclable cardboard booth sends the right message and, in many cases, becomes a conversation starter that draws foot traffic.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Choosing the Right Sheet Specifications</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Wall Panels: Double-Wall BC Flute</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Main booth walls should use 7mm double-wall BC flute for optimal rigidity-to-weight ratio. At 800x1200mm standard panel size, this is easily paintable, printable, and strong enough to support mounted display shelves.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Structural Beams: Triple-Wall or Laminated</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">For header beams and corner posts, use triple-wall 10mm sheets or laminate two double-wall panels back-to-back. This gives the booth top-beam rigidity needed to carry illuminated signage.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Display Surfaces: Single-Wall E-Flute</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Product display shelves and signage backers benefit from smooth E-flute single-wall, which prints crisply and presents a clean surface for vinyl graphics and magnetic accents.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Delivering to Malaysian Exhibition Venues</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Quinocycle routinely delivers cardboard sheet packs to exhibitor staging areas at MITEC, KLCC, MIECC, Setia City Convention Centre, and Sunway Pyramid Convention Centre. Our drivers know the loading bay protocols and can time arrival to your exhibitor move-in slot.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="bg-surface-variant/50 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-8 my-12">
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Exhibition Booth Sheet Specification Guide</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">WALL PANELS</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">7mm BC flute | 800x1200mm | Paintable surface</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">HEADER BEAM</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">10mm triple-wall | 2400x300mm | Rigid span</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">DISPLAY SHELF</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">5mm E-flute | Custom cut | Print-ready</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">FR-TREATED (VENUE RATED)</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">7mm BC + FR coating | Class B fire-rated</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Exhibitor FAQs</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">Can you cut panels to custom dimensions?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Yes. We offer CNC and blade-cut services for custom dimensions and slot-and-tab joinery patterns. Share your booth dimensions and we'll quote materials plus cutting.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">Does the booth look professional or "cardboard-y"?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">With proper graphic treatment — wheat-pasted posters, vinyl wraps, or direct flexo print — cardboard booths are indistinguishable from conventional stands at 1m viewing distance.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">What about lighting and electrics?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Mount LED strip lights with double-sided tape along panel edges. Battery-powered options avoid the need for venue electrical hookups. We can supply cable-management sleeves.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">Can I store the booth for next year's show?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Flat-pack it with protective sleeves. Stored in a dry location, a well-built cardboard booth lasts 5–8 exhibitions. Keep spare panels for cosmetic touch-ups.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">Lead time for custom booth sheet packs?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Standard stock ships within 3 days. Custom-cut packs with CNC joinery require 7–10 business days. Book at least 2 weeks before your exhibition date.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Build Your Next Exhibition Booth for Less</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Quinocycle supplies corrugated sheets to Malaysian SMEs, event agencies, and corporate exhibitors across Peninsular Malaysia. Smart sheet specifications, reliable lead times, competitive wholesale pricing.</p>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface mb-6"><strong>Contact Quinocycle today:</strong></p>
        <ul class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>📞 <strong>Phone:</strong> +60 16 8916 381 / 03-8962 6381</li>
          <li>📧 <strong>Email:</strong> quinocycle@gmail.com</li>
          <li>📍 <strong>Address:</strong> No.13, Jalan Taming P/1, Taming Jaya, Balakong, Selangor 43300</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={WA_LINK} class="inline-block bg-primary text-on-primary font-label font-bold text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">💬 Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Conclusion: Show Up Big, Spend Small</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-4">Cardboard exhibition booths have matured from DIY curiosities into legitimate competitors to traditional stands. Malaysian brands from tech startups to F&B SMEs are using them to punch above their weight at KLCC, MITEC, and regional shows. The cost savings are enormous; the sustainability story is a bonus.</p>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed">Quinocycle has supplied Selangor exhibitors since 2010. Get in touch for your next show.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
